/*
 * Selection, crossover, and mutation
 * 
 * individual = strategy of what to do in certain situations (i.e. always call) 
 * 
 * crossover = take some elements from strategy 1 and some from strategy 2 and form 
 * 				strategy 3
 * mutation = random change in strategy every 5 generations 
 * 
 * fitness = total amount of money won after x (100?) hands
 * 
 * selection = play the population against one another and the 4 fittest produce offspring
 * 
 * generation = train for 9 players first, then 6, then 5, then 4, 3, 2 
 */